Fire a trigger Animator parameter using a serialized binder field — the target Animator is assigned in the Inspector.
The binder exposes the trigger as an  or  on the ViewModel.

    [View]
    public partial class ExampleView
    {
        [SerializeField]
        private AnimatorSetTriggerBinder _jump;
    }
    
    [ViewModel]
    public partial class ExampleViewModel
    {
        [Bind] public IRelayCommand _jump;
    }


